t:
seems so real sometimes?
    They say it's so cause when you're dreaming, you're actually living a alternate reality, a alternate life in a different timeline or in a parallel universe.

However, this terrifies me as
I've never had a dream in
my life.
c:
Or I just had only nightmares...
